Package model.exchanges.events

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActionEvent
    Event sent by the Action View and received from the Action Controller to choose the next action
    ChooseNewtonOpponentEvent
    Event sent by the PowerUp View and received from the PowerUp Controller to choose the target to use the Newton PowerUp on
    ChooseNewtonSquareEvent
    Event sent by the PowerUp View and received from the PowerUp Controller to choose the square to move the chosen Newton target to
    ChoosePickUpWeaponEvent
    Event sent by the Weapon View and received from the Weapon Controller to choose the which weapon to pickup from the current spawn point
    ChoosePowerUpEvent
    Event sent by the PowerUp View and received from the PowerUp Controller to choose which powerUp in the player's resources to use
    ChooseTeleporterSquareEvent
    Event sent by the PowerUp View and received from the PowerUp Controller to choose the square to move the current player to using the teleporter
    ChooseWeaponSquareEvent
    Event sent by the Weapon View and received from the Weapon Controller to choose the square to use for the current weapon's requirements
    DiscardPowerUpEvent
    Event sent by the PowerUp View and received from the PowerUp Controller to choose which powerUp in the player's resources to discard
    Event
    Abstract class extended by all concrete events
    OptionalFireModesEvent
    Event sent by the Weapon View and received from the Weapon Controller to choose which fire mode to select for the current weapon
    PickUpPaymentEvent
    Event sent by the Weapon View and received from the Weapon Controller to choose which powerUps to pay the picked-up weapon with
    QuitAfkEvent
    Event sent by the Action View and received from the Action Controller to choose which one of the AFK players to wake up
    ReloadPaymentEvent
    Event sent by the Weapon View and received from the Weapon Controller to choose which powerUps to pay the selected unloaded weapon with
    ScopePaymentEvent
    Event sent by the PowerUp View and received from the PowerUp Controller to choose which color of cube to use to pay the Targeting Scope PowerUp
    TagbackGrenadeEvent
    Event sent by the PowerUp View and received from the PowerUp Controller to choose which one of the TagBack Grenades in the damaged player's hand to use
    TargetingScopeEvent
    Event sent by the PowerUp View and received from the PowerUp Controller to choose whether to use the Targeting scope or not
    TargetingScopeSelectionEvent
    Event sent by the PowerUp View and received from the PowerUp Controller to choose which target to use the TargetingScope on
    TargetsSelectionEvent
    Event sent by the Weapon View and received from the Weapon Controller to choose which of the given targets to hit
    VoteMapEvent
    Event sent by the Action View and received from the Action Controller to choose which map to vote for
    WeaponPaymentEvent
    Event sent by the Weapon View and received from the Weapon Controller to choose which powerUps to pay the selected fire mode for the current weapon with
    WeaponReloadEvent
    Event sent by the Weapon View and received from the Weapon Controller to choose which of the unloaded weapons in the current player's hand to reload
    WeaponSelectionEvent
    Event sent by the Weapon View and received from the Weapon Controller to choose which of the loaded weapons in the current player's resources to shoot with
    WeaponSwapEvent
    Event sent by the Weapon View and received from the Weapon Controller to choose which weapon in the current player's resources to swap with one on the current spawn point
